user.biography: Home of the Original Glazed Doughnut. 🍩 & ☕ since 1937.  Share sweet moments with #KrispyKreme.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Krispy Kreme Doughnuts on August 18, 2021. May be an image of dessert.

node.text:
Filled with marshmallow Kreme, dipped in @Hersheys chocolate icing, drizzled with more marshmallow Kreme + chocolate icing AND topped with graham cracker crumbs!! 😍 Mood = drooling.

S'mores doughnuts at participating US & CAN shops, WHILE SUPPLIES LAST. All info on doughnuts & shops at link in bio. #krispykreme #doughnuts
